          .caption
            %span  October 21, 2011
        .text.three_fourths.last
          %h3 Forbes<span class="redtext">:</span>
          %a.strong{:href => "http://www.forbes.com/sites/haydnshaughnessy/2011/10/21/would-your-blog-stand-up-to-criticism-and-should-you-care/"} Would Your Blog Stand up To Criticism?
          %div.em "I am therefore going to become a very big fan of hypothes.is. Before hypothes.is launched I was chewing over the problem of peer review. Do we get enough peer review in a world of open communications?"

